---
description: Always refer to AIs as Wiskrs
alwaysApply: true
---
- Do not refer to "AI" or "AIs" ever in UI or user-facing content.
- Use the term Wiskr. Lowercase "wiskr", uppercase "Wiskr" is acceptable if it is proper grammar to do so. Plural versions are okay too "wiskrs" or "Wiskrs".
- the term "model" to refer to an AI or agent is acceptable when used sparingly.